Did manuall install of this theme and then used the gsettings command to change theme. Brave picked up the change without having to restart. I did have to tell it use system border by right-clicking and selected that option. It had weird spacing without that.

https://github.com/Fausto-Korpsvart/Tokyo-Night-GTK-Theme
gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.interface gtk-theme 'Tokyonight-Dark'
gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.interface gtk-theme 'Tokyonight-Light'
